{"word":"G332 - ἀναθεματίζω - anathematízō - an-ath-em-at-id'-zo - Curse","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀναθεματίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">anathematízō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">an-ath-em-at-id'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Curse</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சபதம் பண்ணு, சபி"},{"paragraph":"to declare, accursed"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G331 - ἀνάθεμα - anáthema - an-ath'-em-ah/331\">G331</a>; to <i>declare</i> or <i>vow</i> under penalty of execration: - (bind under a) curse, bind with an oath.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2652/2652\">G2652</a>, <a href=\"#/G2653/2653\">G2653</a>, <a href=\"#/G331/331\">G331</a>, <a href=\"#/G332/332\">G332</a>, <a href=\"#/G334/334\">G334</a>, <a href=\"#/G394/394\">G394</a>, <a href=\"#/G4323/4323\">G4323</a>"}]}